code: function parseErrorToStacks(error){if(!error||!(error instanceof Error)){throw new Error("parseErrorToStacks expects Error object");}if(typeof error.stack==="string"){return error.stack.split("\n").filter(function(stack){return stack!=="Error: ".concat(error.message);});}}function listenToRuntimeError(callback){window.addEventListener("error",callback);return function cleanup(){window.removeEventListener("error",callback);};}function listenToUnhandledRejection(callback){window.addEventListener("unhandledrejection",callback);return function cleanup(){window.removeEventListener("unhandledrejection",callback);};}export{listenToRuntimeError,listenToUnhandledRejection,parseErrorToStacks};
